{"tid":2069941,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"扮係另一個女仔成功溝到追左好耐既人但唔敢出街","createTime":"2020-06-18T19:04:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-19T09:57:07.000Z","uid":142854,"like":4,"dislike":43,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"8c29ab22edd234596bcbe7ba0c33db68d8091077","tid":2069941,"uid":142854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T19:04:39.000Z","msg":"由六年前中學開始追佢<br />\n到而家出黎做左一年野<br />\n我都用自己個WhatsApp keep住同佢聯絡<br />\n<br />\n我講左好耐好多次鐘意佢<br />\n佢一開始話要專心讀書<br />\nDse後話要考慮<br />\nGrad完後就話返工好忙<br />\n到今時今日都唔肯應我既好意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係兩三個月前我用一個新開telegram搵佢<br />\n扮係一個係行山識既女仔(我知佢成日行山)<br />\n之後我地好好傾 因為我知道哂佢既興趣<br />\n例如聽歌 食野 運動等等方面既野<br />\n而且我地成日同聲同氣 佢都講點解可以搵到個咁夾既人<br />\n有好多時佢覆完tg都唔會覆我正身既WhatsApp<br />\n<br />\n之後佢不斷咁想我同佢交換相<br />\n但我都轉移話題<br />\n直至頭先佢係tg同我表白<br />\n話咁多年黎都未搵過一個咁岩既女仔<br />\n無論我係咩樣咩條件都想做我男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲約我聽日出街<br />\n但係我唔知點樣見佢。。。<br />\n好驚佢見到我調頭走失望個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n應該點算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj